"Hey, watch what you say to the Predacon Commander Scorponok.  If there is a 
remote chance for you to join us, Scorponok here may be your only ticket in. 
I'd suggest you two be more respectful to him."

She lowered her dagger again.

"Now all of you knock it off. This is no way for us to act if we are to work 
together."

She looked up at Megatron who was still standing next to them waiting for 
Panzertron. "Megatron, I wait your command, my commander."
